{"type":null,"faqId":48178,"title":"Mate S在阳光下屏幕会变鲜艳，在阳光下亮度会突然变亮？","answer":"您好，在阳光下或者外界光线很强烈的时候，Mate S手机会自动开启阳光下可视的功能，如下图，给人的感觉是亮度会突然变亮，而且屏幕的颜色会有轻微变化，黑色会变成偏灰色，其他颜色也会变得更加鲜艳亮丽一些，这是手机自带的功能，并不是手机的故障，目前此功能是默认开启的，只要感应到外界光线强度达到一定的程度就会开启，没有关闭的开关。","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":1,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3843","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1446428710000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10,CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":69,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}